com.nokia.mid.ui.multipointtouch
Interface MultipointTouchListener

public interface MultipointTouchListener

This interface is used by applications which need to receive multipoint touch events from the implementation. An application will provide an implementation of a MulitpointTouchListener (typically by using a nested class or an inner class).

Method Summary
 void pointersChanged(int[] pointerIds)
          Indicates that the state and/or coordinates of one or more touch points have changed.
 

Method Detail

pointersChanged

void pointersChanged(int[] pointerIds)

Indicates that the state and/or coordinates of one or more touch points have changed.

Parameters:
